est','Easy to use and elegant in design. Perfect Gift for Kids.',1,0,2815),(3439,5,'Great product','Our daughter loves her new tablet. It has a bigger screen more features and she just enjoys being on it. The kindle is priced right and is easy to use. She was able to get her apps transferred to her new tablet in no time. Great investment.',1,0,2816),(3440,4,'Great tablet','Love this tablet easy to use and extremely affordable',1,0,865),(3441,5,'Great tablet','Got this tablet for my mother and liked it so much that I went and got one for myself! It runs fast for what I use it for!',1,0,1923),(3442,5,'Great Tablet','Great tablet for price. Display is clear. Enjoy books on tablet.',1,0,1645),(3443,5,'Works great','Definitely an amazing deal at an amazing price on Black Friday weekend',1,0,2817),(3444,4,'Better than the Kindle HD 7','Improved over the HD 7. Things set up differently but not hard to learn. Also a bit heavier than the 7 so reading in bed a little harder',1,1,2818),(3445,5,'Great tablet','I was looking for a kids tablet for my grandson but this one is so much better because it can grow with him and it has a kids mode on it which is really nice so he can\'t order or go online without permission. He loves this tablet and it\'s very well build .',1,0,2819),(3446,5,'Great tablet','I love this tablet! love my ipad , too, but this is much lighter weight and easier to slip in my purse. I went for a 32g but there were none in stock, so I got the 16 and a memory card that I will probably never need!',1,0,812),(3447,1,'Ended up returning','I bought this tablet for my 4 year old daughter. Too many advertisements. I would rather pay more and not have a single ad.',0,2,2820),(3448,5,'Amazon HD 8','I bought this kindle for the extra size. I have recently been having trouble with seeing clearly so I figured with the size it may be easier. It was and I really like being able to change the color of the fonts and background, it seems to help immensely.',1,0,2407),(3449,4,'Works as advertised, but the ads get annoying','As far as functionality it works well. I can surf the internet, match movies, check social media, and anything else a tablet is supposed to do. The app store has a good variety off apps. It does not have as many as the iTunes store, but there is plenty of variety. The reason I knock a star off is the constant ads. I know that this is an Amazon product, but the ads get a little annoying.',1,0,2821),(3450,5,'Nice tablet for amazon users','Bought this for someone as a gift. They are big on amazon kindle so this was a huge plus with other features and amazon store improving. They love it.I know other tablets have kindle apps but this was an awesome price.',1,0,2822),(3451,5,'Easy to use tablet','Very easy to use and has so much to offer for the low price.',1,0,2823),(3452,5,'Perfect for summer reading and movies','This was an upgrade purchase. My previous Kindle was 4 years old. (still working!) This new version is so much faster and has a much better quality camera! Love it for reading, Netflix and on-line shopping!',1,0,548),(3453,4,'Nice 8 tablet','This tablet is easy to use and great for a new user.',1,0,2824),(3454,5,'Great tablet','This is a great tablet for kids and adults alike.!',1,0,2825),(3455,4,'Nice','I purchased this as a gift and I\'m had I did. This tablet far exceeds my expectations.',1,0,2826),(3456,5,'Great first tablet!','This is a great tablet for my teen. She loves it and the price can\'t be beat!',1,1,2827),(3457,5,'Excellent for what it does it','Excellent product for what it does. Spouse loves it!Nough said!',1,0,2828),(3458,5,'Good battery','We like the battery endurance. The new 8\" screen is great too.',1,0,2829),(3459,5,'Kids tablet','Great Christmas gifts for the kids. Hours of fun and games.',1,0,2830),(3460,5,'Great budget tablet','Definitely worth the investment...I may get a couple of more!',1,0,2831),(3461,4,'Easy to use','Easy to use tablet. Price is pretty good. My mom loves it.',1,0,160