ing it also & he likes it. He has never used a tablet before but he has enjoyed it.',1,0,3164),(3861,5,'Great value!','For under $100 this 8\" tablet is a bargain. I do all I want on it like; check email, Facebook, Twitter, watch YouTube, read books, and shop on eBay or Amazon. I\'ve been very pleased with my purchase.',1,0,3165),(3862,4,'Great as a gift they love it better than paper bac','This was a gift for a family member they really enjoy all the options of getting books',1,0,3166),(3863,5,'The Kindle Fire 8 is awesome!','I purchased the Kindle Fire 8\" after owning a 7\" for several years. I love the bigger screen and added features in this version.',1,0,3167),(3864,4,'Okay, but not the best','It\'s actually a very good product for a decent price. Not lightning fast but it is okay for everyday use.',1,0,3168),(3865,5,'great Christmas gift','Gave as Christmas gift,and wife loved it. She has not put it down since she has gotten it.',1,0,3169),(3866,4,'good tablet for the price.','this Amazon fire tab works really well.the syncing aspect is very nice being able to pair it with all my devices.i wish it had Google play.',1,0,740),(3867,5,'Ok','I thought that this tablet was junk but it has surpassed my expectations',1,0,3170),(3868,5,'MY AMAZON FIRE ROCKS','I HAVE BEEN WITH AMAZON PRIME FOR 2 YEARS AND THIS NEW FIRE HD MAKES IT WORTH IT. i WATCH MOVIES WHEN I FLY BECAUSE I CAN DOWNLOAD THEM. THE BATTERY LAST FOR DAYS. I USE IT EVERYDAY NOW.',1,0,3171),(3869,4,'One flaw','Not sure if this is due to the new version but I\'m not able to install or even sideload certain apps onto the tablet. Amazon is really trying to lock out non-Amazon apps namely ones from Google. Aside from that though, performance is already and what you\'d expect from a tablet in this price range. This was purchased for my mom and it does what\'s needed and my mom has no complaints thus far.',1,1,17),(3870,5,'Great tablet','Love this tablet. Bought it to be my touch screen remote for my harmony h